						               													<description>The most fun and tasty game, now playable with up to 4 players! Gather all the different candies and hurry up to be the first to collect the cherry. Test your creativity and create a magical chain of candies to reach the cherry in the middle of the game board. But be aware of your opponents, because when 3 of the same candies connect, your plan will fall apart! Is luck on your side and are you tactical enough to win the candy crush board game?&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Candy Crush the board game is a 2 to 4 players strategic board game. The game is played with 6 dice all containing 6 different colors of candies. Players roll all dice a maximum of three times in their turn and try to roll as many of the same colors. Depending on the dice result, players place a number of candy tokens on the board. These can be place either on their own board or that of their opponents. The first player to reach the cherry in the middle of the board by placing enough candy tokens wins the game. But remember that your candy tokens will disappear when an opponent places 3 of the same candies on your board.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;-description from publisher&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
